{
  "stem": "14251.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They would probably break down everything surrounding the door, and the door would remain standing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we had what we called an emergency exit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "A desk had, on the inside of the little unit, been placed against the wall.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And underneath it was the hole.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And from the other side, a bunch of rubble had been placed, like ashes, broken dishes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And of course, one of the Gestapo men had shot into that idly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Well, that just took minutes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because when-- when you shoot into a pile like that, idly or not, what happened was that the whole pile collapsed and exposed the exit hole that was supposed to be the emergency exit if they came in through the wardrobe and all that.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that's-- I've since heard other wardrobe stories.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Other people had the same ideas that came to all of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Well, in came-- I don't know if it was four or five plainclothesmen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And for years, I avoided all people with green Tyrolean hats.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Remember, hats used to be worn by men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And it-- particularly, if they had a little brush up here, like a shaving brush almost-- feathers, looking like a Tyrolean.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And coats and all that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And there they stood with their revolvers in their hand.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
